<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <title>看乐可旅行直播，送旅行好礼</title>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, user-scalable=0, minimum-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0">
    <meta name="format-detection" content="telephone=no" />
    <link rel='stylesheet' href='stylesheets/success.css' />

  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="top-img">
      <img src="images/lalocal.png" alt="乐可旅行标志" />
    </div>
    <div class="banner">
      <img src="images/successTop.png" alt="首页顶部图" />
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <div class="coupon">
        <img src="images/lalocalCoupon.png" alt="乐可优惠券" / class="lalocalCoupon">
        <h6>乐可旅行</h6>
        <div class="display-sesize"></div>
        <img src="images/wanziCoupon.png" alt="丸子优惠券" / class="wanziCoupon">
        <h6>乐可旅行</h6>
      </div>
      <div class="display-sesize"></div>
      <div class="btn-group">
        <img src="images/cashBtn.png" alt="立即兑换" / class="cashBtn">
        <img src="images/downBtn.png" alt="下载使用" / class="downBtn">
        <img src="images/shareBtn.png" alt="微信分享" / class="shareBtn">
      </div>
      <div class="active-rule">
        <img src="images/activeRule.png" alt="活动规则" />
        <p>
          1.旅行基金新老用户共享 <br>
          2.旅行基金可与其他优惠叠加使用<br>
          3.旅行基金可在订单提交时直接输入优惠码抵扣相应现金<br>
          4.仅限App在线支付使用<br>
          5.单个优惠码仅与一个手机号捆绑使用<br>
          6.其他未尽事宜，请咨询客服<br>
          7.活动时间：2016.9.25-2016.9.30
        </p>
        <div class="display-sesize"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="display-sesize"></div>
  </body>

  <%include include_share.ejs %>
  <script type="text/javascript">
    window.onload = function () {
      var flag = '<%=flag%>';
      if(flag == true){
        $('.downBtn').show();
        $('.cashBtn').hide();
      }
    }
    $('.downBtn').on('click',function () {
      window.location.href = 'http://a.app.qq.com/o/simple.jsp?pkgname=com.lalocal.lalocal';
    })
    $('.shareBtn').on('click',function () {
      window.location.href = 'share';
    })
  </script>
</html>
